Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:33.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:40.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:53.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:01:00.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:04.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.17,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:15.22,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:28.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:33.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:43.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:50.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界格蘭披治大賽的預選賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既將在富士賽站舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在預選賽前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新車阿斯拉達從海外運送來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知什麼原因而被迫截
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在千鈞一髮之際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四歲的風見隼人及時保衛車子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把車安全運送到賽車場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 你的聲紋和角膜已被我記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你以外的車手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能開動這部車的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二話  最年輕的賽車手誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 我似乎做了不可挽回的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意 這不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 這不是隼人的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想得那麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介一定會順利完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車手的記錄還未能修改過來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個程式很難從外面連接的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了…被鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個保護程式似乎有點棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是若不在今天辦妥的話 比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉! 這樣是不能開動車子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等伸介改好程式後再算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我車匙 我要再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統啟動 開始檢查駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我聽你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我不能開動這車?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查完畢 你的聲紋和角膜狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我所儲存的記錄不吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 你不能開動我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這車隊的車手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啟動引擎 蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很可惜 似乎和你沒有緣份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了 一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天這樣努力至通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得一身油污的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是為了明天的比賽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 真丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父不是夢想自己親手做的車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站在世界的頂點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這種狀況也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我破壞了大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒坐上那部車 便不會搞成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果隼人沒把車送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們車隊根本不能出場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人做得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉 等等 在這裏等老闆來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時 不 三十分鐘便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你們照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉先生你要離開嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯我明天不能出賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已沒必要再在這逗留了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用以前的賽車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些沒勁的車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕連預選賽也不能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物能勝過阿斯拉達嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭倦了小鬼頭的遐想了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我… 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一早知道記錄系統的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫你把車子帶到安全地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有任何責任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督 爸爸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到車裏再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 在這種地方幹什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員全都回車上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在檢查賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很謹慎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車是不能大意的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我有點在意那部車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是營生車隊的新車阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那弱小車隊的車…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見已實踐了十年前的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年前的約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做車手 你負責機械修理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見負責設計
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人合力進軍世界頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已登場了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的圍牆不是太厚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的夢想卻不能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在車隊解散時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾對我這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能勝出是因為我設計的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的技術還不熟練
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後風見便去了美國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了發明不輸給任何人的導航系統「CYBER SYSTEM」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營生 我製造了不得了的「CYBER SYSTEM」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前只要裝置了「CYBER SYSTEM」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便一定能勝出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完成了那個以後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現有點危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危機?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要搶奪「CYBER SYSTEM」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 詳情現在還不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營生 再一起實現以前三人的夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要推出賽車是裝了此系統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳媒也能扮演監視者的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那你打算怎辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時隱藏起來 至於隼人的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的事不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會負責保護他和車子的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輛車今後一切就由我來接手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的事也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法回答太抽像的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我與選擇標準
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車以外的事也能理解嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失禮 好 請問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒車手而棄權富士崗預選賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是由我這個外行人出場好呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案很清楚簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加預選賽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進軍決賽的夢想並非等於零
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是零?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監督聽爸爸說了有關車子的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達GXX 並非一般的「CYBER FORMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何製作都會保留一點秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如保護系統也是因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天的比賽怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要棄權嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算讓隼人駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是參加預選賽嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才趕及車檢 我想試一試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這部車和以前的有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想看看它在賽道上奔馳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能通過預選也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你覺得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦子好混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在很難回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用現在回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有點時間可以考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就看隼人的意願了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若大家認為我可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是營生車隊的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是車手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家都賭註明天的比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別太過期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說大家也沒期待什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很老實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這樣決定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備明天的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去更換賽車的零件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試駕駛一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 張開口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要問 照著做就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有蛀牙 好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼問蛀牙的事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車手身體負荷很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了忍耐便要咬緊牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蛀牙便不能好好咬著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且亦能判斷車手的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蛀牙生活肯定不太好 明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位合適嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的視力怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右眼都是1.5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間緊迫 只會給你一點意見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了後今天好好休息 為了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快便完成輸入賽道資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給阿斯拉達了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:13:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人雖然有點亂來 但沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起的車子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平 拿著螺旋鉗 良平!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非今晚完成不可 沒時間發呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遲 但還算趕得及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 不見良平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成整備後便整個人鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 很快會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦? 沒可能會勝出的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好看嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很有型啊 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 但找這個尺碼也真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是人靠衣裝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣車手也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美紀做引擎的最後檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介負責檢查無線電
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條先生 早晨 新條先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說一下今天預賽的抱負
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早便這麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信心在今天預賽中排頭位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非那人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他是新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐洲兩屆冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看比賽 我不會辜負大家的期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 訪問就到此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請比賽完後再繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條先生 請再說多一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨 今日子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來新車趕得及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車手好像換了呢 是那小子嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車並不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要妨礙其他車手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你爸爸發明的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER SYSTEM」的車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護身符 不要胡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.04,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的 不要受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出賽道後要握緊方向盤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的跟從阿斯拉達去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我現在圈速的時間資料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 新條君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會取得頭位的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意路面狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 只是有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近第一個彎道 快進入彎位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意煞車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這車的速度真是很快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近第二個彎了 重煞車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達駛離了跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳 真痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼轉不到彎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超速了 你煞車太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼優越的車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不在轉彎時不減速是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 初次比賽 也沒法子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 車子有受損嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子不容許受損的 沒有異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就返回賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 安全返回賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已返回賽道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車手和車都正常 沒有損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎? 隼人 聽見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個圈開始計時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次比賽不要亂來 明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 準備測量圈速
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美紀準備換車胎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父 對不起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著會很忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先來準備車胎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 進入最後彎位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

